item.title: TME
item.description: score:36 Chances: Tencent Music Entertainment Group (TME) has renewed its strategic licensing agreement with Universal Music Group, showcasing a continued commitment to creating value for artists and music lovers. The shift towards streaming stocks could present a significant opportunity for TME, as traditional distribution channels continue to decline.
